# Data License
=============

This project uses the **“Food Vendors”** dataset from the **City of Vancouver
Open Data Portal**:

- Dataset: Food Vendors  
- URL: https://opendata.vancouver.ca/explore/dataset/food-vendors/table/

The data is published under the **Open Government Licence – Vancouver**.
See: https://opendata.vancouver.ca/pages/licence/

Please attribute the City of Vancouver as the data provider when re-using or
sharing any results based on this dataset.

